    <element name="Earth Fist" type="Spell" source="Omeria" id="ID_DMDAVE_OMERIA_SPELL_EARTH_FIST">
        <supports>Druid, Elementalist, Sorcerer, Warlock, Wizard, Spell Saving Throw</supports>
        <description>
            <p>The ground at a point within range sprouts an earthen arm which remains for the duration.</p>
            <p class="indent">The arm is an object that has AC 17 and hit points equal to 3 x your caster level. If it drops to 0 hit points, the spell ends. It has a Strength of 20 (+5) and a Dexterity of 9 (-1). The arm doesn’t fill its space.</p>
            <p class="indent">When you cast the spell and as a bonus action on your subsequent turns, you can cause one of the following effects with it.</p>
            <p class="indent"><strong><em>Move.</em></strong> The arm moves up to 20 feet to a space that you can see within 60 feet of you and sprouts out of the ground there. It does not provoke attacks of opportunity when it moves. </p>
            <p class="indent"><strong><em>Slam.</em></strong> The arm makes a melee spell attack against a target within 5 feet of it. On a hit, the target takes 2d8 bludgeoning damage. </p>
            <p class="indent"><strong><em>Grab.</em></strong> The arm attempts to grapple a Medium or smaller creature within 5 feet of it. You use the arm’s Strength score to resolve the grapple. While the hand is grappling the target, you can use a bonus action to have the hand crush it. When you do so, the target takes 2d6 bludgeoning damage. </p>
            <p class="indent"><strong><em>At Higher Levels.</em></strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the damage from the slam option increases by 1d6, and the damage from the grab option increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 3rd. </p>
        </description>
        <setters>
            <set name="keywords">bludgeoning</set>
            <set name="level">3</set>
            <set name="school">Transmutation</set>
            <set name="time">1 action</set>
            <set name="range">120 feet</set>
            <set name="duration">Concentration up to 1 minute</set>
            <set name="hasVerbalComponent">true</set>
            <set name="hasSomaticComponent">true</set>
            <set name="hasMaterialComponent">true</set>
            <set name="materialComponent">five small pieces of crystal</set>
            <set name="isConcentration">true</set>
            <set name="isRitual">false</set>
        </setters>
    </element>
    <element name="Earth Shield" type="Spell" source="Omeria" id="ID_DMDAVE_OMERIA_SPELL_EARTH_SHIELD">
        <supports>Druid, Ranger</supports>
        <description>
            <p>You conjure an earthen shield which forms around your arm. For the duration, you gain 15 temporary hit points, including against the triggering attack.</p>
            <p class="indent"><strong><em>At Higher Levels.</em></strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, you gain an additional 10 temporary hit points for each slot level above 1st. </p>
